# Release packages (kept on-repo for direct download; see release/SHA256SUMS.txt)
# NOTE: each release adds ~134 KB of binary blob to git history with no LFS or
# cleanup. For multi-year repos consider moving zips to .gitattributes + Git LFS.
*.zip
!release/*.zip
!release/SHA256SUMS*
